ADF DESIGN:-
Schedule Trigger — run daily. 
Lookup / Get Control Value — read last successful file watermark. 
Set Variable — set new high watermark for this run. 
Copy Activity — copy only new/changed files using LastModifiedDate. 
If Condition — run downstream only if files were copied. 
Databricks Notebook Activity — run row-level incremental transformation and SCD2 logic. 
Stored Procedure / Script Activity — update watermark on success.
Audit Log Activity — insert audit details.
Failure Branch — log error + send alert + do not move watermark. 
